From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: MC20018 <winme2001@outlook.com>
Date: Mon, 8 Jun 2026 14:13:10 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Expand extended ecosystem event hooks

Add vanilla hook points for portal traversal, player world changes, command completions, creative inventory packets, merchant trade preparation and completion, dropped item lifecycle, hanging entity placement and breakage, item frame edits, resource-pack responses, client brand reports, locale changes, and vehicle lifecycle events.

Keep patched code thin by routing API wrapping, cancellation handling, and listener failure logging through Fand bridge helpers.

